data.description: New Construction home. All the amenities you are looking for at a great price! The Grove is conveniently located just 5 miles off Hwy 11 and 4 miles off Hwy 411. This craftsman style home features a covered front porch, open deck overlooking the back yard and is on a great level lot. Interior features include hardwood floors, stainless appliances and stone counter tops. The Master suite has a large walk in closet, free standing soaking tub, and separate tile shower. There are more lots and plans to choose from.
